      "writtenOn": "2018-09-17T15:56:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Aside: I find the \"local\" vs. \"remote\" naming to be confusing. Naively I would assume \"remote\" runs on the DUT and \"local\" runs on my workstation.",
